    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3 (E46), a driver\u2019s specification featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine with its signature individual throttle bodies. This example is technically sound, having undergone critical preventative maintenance including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul to ensure timing precision. The drivetrain features the sought-after 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox, delivering power to the rear wheels via a factory limited-slip differential. Suspension dynamics are sharp thanks to refreshed bushings and a set of Bilstein dampers that maintain the chassis's legendary poise. The exterior shows minor road-derived patina consistent with its mileage, but the structural integrity and powertrain performance remain top-tier. Recent compression and leak-down tests confirm the S54 is healthy and pulling strong to its 8,000 RPM redline.",
